### Admin Management Tests

### 1. Get all users (admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 2. Get all drivers (admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/drivers
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3. Create a new driver (admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/drivers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Mike Driver",
  "email": "mike.driver@sendit.com",
  "password": "driver123",
  "phone": "+1555123456",
  "vehicle": "Ford Transit Van"
}

### 4. Create a new admin (admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/admins
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Sarah Admin",
  "email": "sarah.admin@sendit.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 5. Update driver status (admin only)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/admin/drivers/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 6. Get system statistics (admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7. Get all parcels with details (admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/parcels
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8. Update user role (admin only)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/admin/users/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "role": "DRIVER"
} 